'''Revenue Technology Solutions''' began as a division [[Control Data Corporation]]. It developed a [[Yield management|yield management system]] for [[Republic Airlines]] on a mainframe in 1982. Revenue Technology Services Corporation was spun off as an independent company through a purchase by YMS, Inc. in 1991.

Revenue Technology Services provides global revenue management and profit optimization software and consulting services.  The verticals supported are airlines, cargo, coach, cruise/ferry lines, and railroads. Delivered products include revenue management for passenger and cargo, pricing management and business intelligence / analytics.{{citation needed|date=March 2013}}

