'''zColo''' is a wholly owned subsidiary of [[Zayo Group]], operating the colocation and data center services. zColo's principal service offering is colocation space and power with carrier-neutral [[data center]] and interconnection services. As of May 2015, they operate 35 colocation facilities in North America and 8 in Europe.
